OL,3,C'He lied and lied again': Prosecution
OL,4,Cdelivers closing statement in murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe prosecution in the trial of a man
OL,8,Faccused of the murder of Natalie
OL,9,FMcNally told the jury that the
OL,10,Fdefendant "lied and lied again".
OL,12,FStephen McCullagh, 36, of Woodland
OL,13,FGardens in Lisburn denies the charge.
OL,15,FDuring the prosecution's closing
OL,16,Fstatements, the court heard how there
OL,17,Fwere "lies wherever you look" as he
OL,18,F"continued to peddle the false alibi
OL,19,Fof live streaming because he murdered
OL,20,FNatalie McNally."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
