OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773861071
OL,3,C'He lied and lied again': Prosecution
OL,4,Cdelivers closing statement in murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe 32-year-old was found strangled,
OL,8,Fbeaten and stabbed to death in her
OL,9,FLurgan home on 18th December 2022.
OL,11,FShe was 15 weeks pregnant.
OL,13,FThe court heard that the defendant
OL,14,Fchose not to give evidence and how not
OL,15,Fgiving evidence "is an important part
OL,16,Fof the trial".
OL,18,FThe court was told it was a failure to
OL,19,Fgive an innocent explanation because
OL,20,F"there is no answer he could ever give
OL,21,Fthat would stand up to scrutiny."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
