OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773861071
OL,3,C'He lied and lied again': Prosecution
OL,4,Cdelivers closing statement in murder
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe prosecution put it to the jury
OL,8,F"why would you not give evidence if
OL,9,Fyou were innocent?"
OL,11,FMr McCullagh denies murdering Ms
OL,12,FMcNally.
OL,14,FThe defence is due to give their
OL,15,Fclosing statements on Thursday.
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
